      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for this awesome car! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend trip. It drives like a dream and has clearly been well-cared for. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready to go, this is the one! Drop me a message if you're interested\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
