      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This unit retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response facilitated by its individual throttle bodies and double VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, delivering the communicative feedback expected of this platform. While the body shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is dialed in for immediate performance.",
